HEADWORD: Congruence
<hw>Con"gru*ence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>congruentia</ets>: cf. OF. <ets>cornguence</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Suitableness of one thing to another; agreement; consistency.</def>
